  },
  "designedRepetition": {
    "description": "Deliberate cross-thread repetition that must never be reported by any rule: findings whose match lies inside one of these phrases are suppressed. The 15 sensory rhymes are listed for 5.3 editorial reference; they carry no mechanical rule yet.",
